data.title: Players Named For Vince Carter Charity Basketball Game
data.meta_description: Players Announced For 2002 Vince Carter Charity All-Star Game (July 19, 2002) -- Vince Carter announced Friday a preliminary list of NBA players set to hit the hardwood at Air Canada Centre on August 2 at 7:30 pm for the second annual Vince Carter Charity All-Star basketball game, presented by Air Canada.
